```{r}
library(tidyverse)
abess = read_csv('results/abess.csv')
omp = read_csv('results/omp.csv')
```

```{r}
df = abess %>% 
  select(-...1) %>% 
  bind_rows(omp)
```

```{r}
df %>% 
  filter(n<=300) %>% 
  mutate(across(n,as.factor)) %>% 
  ggplot(aes(n,accuracy,fill = method)) +
    geom_boxplot() 
 
```
